--------------------------------------- The Model is using for detecting tough signal ----------------------------------------------

-------------- Input --------------

Current_Filter : the current of each motor mapping from controller to model;

Delay_Time : Delay Time to detection the change of the current and the current delay time before;

Minimun_Limit : Minimum limit of the current change;

State : State is from the control model, represent the leg state, and State == 2 means the control model need the touch signal;

Number : Number is from the control model, and it is the representation of which three legs need to get touch signals;
